 takeover had been set for completion on Friday and will come as a huge 
blow to the One Direction singer who is a lifelong Doncaster supporter.

Tomlinson 
played for their reserve side against Scunthorpe earlier this year and 
had been close to a takeover before, but a move was twice delayed 
